Steps for Creating Spotify Clone

* Firebase - Create new project
- npm install -g firebase-tools

> Deploy to Firebase Hosting
- firebase login
- firebase init
- firebase deploy

Project Console: https://console.firebase.google.com/project/spotify-clone-999cd/overview
Hosting URL: https://spotify-clone-999cd.web.app


* Spotify - (https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard/applications/d150c4a33461402c8f32b17c9eefe2ad)
- ClientID:  d150c4a33461402c8f32b17c9eefe2ad

* Installed the following
- npm i spotify-web-api-js

* Material UI - (https://material-ui.com/)
- npm install @material-ui/core
- npm install @material-ui/icons